…Nothing Will Stop Us From Taking Over Power In 2023 – Ayu ABUJA – The Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) has officially thrown the presidential contest open. This is even as the former President of the Senate, David Mark was appointed to chair the party presidential primary scheduled to hold on the 28th of May, 2022. -Advertisement- Recall that the party had in the past months embroiled in crisis over where the presidential ticket should be zoned to. While the southern stakeholders of the party were of the opinion that the ticket should be zoned to South, their Northern counterparts said that the contest should be thrown open.